                                        ></a><a class="xref"></a>&#124; <img src="images/Icon_2.jpg"
                                        alt="image" /></p>
                                <div class="caption"><p>Holistic Marketing Dimensions</p></div>
                            </figcaption>
                        </figure>
                    </article>
                </article>
