                                    </ul>
                                    <p><span class="strong">Purchasing</span></p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li><p>They proactively search for the best suppliers.</p></li>
                                        <li><p>They build long-term relationships with fewer but more
                                                reliable, high-quality suppliers.</p></li>
                                        <li><p>They don&#8217;t compromise quality for price
